casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Mondrut.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Mondrut (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 1204.]

(No. 91-1862 Submitted October 9, 1991 Decided October 10, 1991.)

The resignation of George Andrew Mondrut as an attorney, Registration No. 0001294, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
